    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EStructuralFeature.Internal.DynamicValueHolder, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, ActuatorSystem, CyberPhysicalSystem, LocomotionSystem, RoboticSystem, SteeredWheelSystem, System

    public class SteeredWheelSystemImpl
extends LocomotionSystemImpl
implements SteeredWheelSystem
    An implementation of the model object 'Steered Wheel System'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Wheel Radius
    • Wheel Width
    • Suspension Rest Length
    • Wheel Connection Height
    • Type Of Wheel
    • Wheel Velocity PI Dkp
    • Wheel Velocity PI Dki
    • Wheel Velocity PI Dkd
    • Wheel Steering PI Dkp
    • Wheel Steering PI Dkd
    • Wheel Friction
    • Suspension Stiffness
    • Suspension Damping
    • Suspension Compression
    • Wheel Velocity PI Dmax Sum
    • Wheel Velocity PI Dmax Val
